title: Power Football, Creed, and ‘What's more likely?’
itunes:title: Power Football, Creed, and ‘What's more likely?’
description:
A room full of heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling, Marc Sessler and Lindsay Rhodes –  break down the latest stories from the NFL, including Jalen Ramsey’s knee injury and if power football is making a comeback. Then the heroes discuss the Around the NFL edition of the Top 100 players of 2016 before wrapping the podcast playing “What’s more likely?” Plus, is it a Creed song?
